com.sleepycat.client

Interface GetHelper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCursor, SDatabase, SSecondaryCursor, SSecondaryDatabase

    public interface GetHelper
    GetHelper implements a few helper methods for making remote get / pGet calls.
